TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement SELECT cast(name as varchar(20)) name, value from ( SELECT TOP 99.99999999 PERCENT cast(last_modified_datetime as date) name, cast(COUNT(*) as varchar(20)) as value FROM LSW_BPD_INSTANCE where last_modified_datetime >= DATEADD(DAY, -7, GETDATE()) and create_datetime >= DATEADD(DAY, -7, GETDATE()) GROUP BY cast(last_modified_datetime as date) order by cast(last_modified_datetime as date)) as taba1

tw.local.sqlStatement SELECT VARCHAR_FORMAT(DATE_TRUNC('DAY', create_datetime), 'YYYY/MM/DD') name, cast(COUNT(*) as char(20)) as value FROM LSW_BPD_INSTANCE where create_datetime >= date(CURRENT TIMESTAMP -7 DAY) and last_modified_datetime >= date(CURRENT TIMESTAMP -7 DAY) GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('DAY', create_datetime) order by DATE_TRUNC('DAY', create_datetime)
